{"tid":1510300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒 肯籌備臨時政府同立會未？","createTime":"2019-08-27T06:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T07:41:32.000Z","uid":18648,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f609001075fd4399f554a2ba5ff306c7282cdbd","tid":1510300,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"好明顯港共已經再唔需要民意<br />\n佢輸晒民意對佢根本係零傷害<br />\n<br />\n佢話唔會回應我地嘅訴求<br />\n當下最有效嘅抗爭除左武裝起義<br />\n就係成立臨時政府同立會<br />\n點都好過個個星期都鳩行之後鳩打<br />\n之後一大班手足被捕<br />\n<br />\n唔好再講話無軍隊無槍無炮哩類廢話<br />\n依家無軍隊 我地就自組軍隊<br />\n我地無槍無炮 睇下烏克蘭點解決 再參考<br />\n<br />\n解放軍入黎 我第一個出去同佢死過<br />\n佢打過黎 我地就武裝<br />\n<br />\n要快<br />\n要快<br />\n要快<br />\n<br />\n遲多一兩日<br />\n就多十幾二十個手足犧牲"},{"pid":"c4221f3d3d9c84a44a869acfcb11eaa25936a188","tid":1510300,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=d39841e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=ba981444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=4d98f981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"83b9a9b0827aaa9a41e84c4d4b746fb5ca707a3c","tid":1510300,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl